title: Astronomy and Astrophysics Midterm Symposium
desc: The symposium will be divided into five topical sections that will each include two fifteen-minute talks followed by a panel discussion. Welcome Talk 1 - Talk 2 - Panel Discussion Moderator: ? The closest airport to the Beckman Center is John Wayne Orange County Airport (SNA). Parking is available on-site at no charge and consists of 172 regular spaces, 5 handicapped spaces, and 100 overflow spaces. For questions about the event, please contact Dionna Williams at dwilliams@nas.edu.
